    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6">

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-[14px] font-bold text-ink">What does the free plan cover?</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-[13px] text-body leading-relaxed">All 400+ skills, 190+ agents, 50 workspace stacks, 41 MCP configs, and 5 language packs. Install via npm (<code class="bg-white px-1 rounded text-[11px] font-mono">npx claudient add all</code>) or the Claude Code plugin marketplace. No credit card, no time limit, no usage caps.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-[14px] font-bold text-ink">How does Team billing work?</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-[13px] text-body leading-relaxed">You pay per active seat per month. A seat is a unique user who signs in to the Team workspace in a given month. Add or remove users anytime — you're only charged for active seats. Annual prepayment gets 15% off.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-[14px] font-bold text-ink">Can I upgrade anytime?</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-[13px] text-body leading-relaxed">Yes. Upgrade from Community → Team → Business → Enterprise anytime. Billing adjusts prorated. Downgrade anytime with 30 days notice. Private stacks are archived but not deleted.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-[14px] font-bold text-ink">Is there a free trial?</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-[13px] text-body leading-relaxed">All teams get a 14-day free trial of Team tier. No credit card required. For Business and Enterprise, contact sales for a guided demo and custom trial.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-[14px] font-bold text-ink">What languages are supported?</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-[13px] text-body leading-relaxed">Community, Team, and Business include English (EN), French (FR), German (DE), Spanish (ES), and Dutch (NL). Enterprise supports custom language packs.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-[14px] font-bold text-ink">How do governance hooks work?</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-[13px] text-body leading-relaxed">Hooks log every time a skill is invoked: who ran it, when, on which file, and what was output. Useful for compliance audits and usage analytics. Included in Business+ tiers with SSO integration.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-[14px] font-bold text-ink">Can we use Claudient offline?</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-[13px] text-body leading-relaxed">Community skills are files in <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded text-[11px] font-mono">~/.claude/</code> and work fully offline. Team+ depends on subscription tier. Self-hosted Enterprise supports complete air-gapped offline mode.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-[14px] font-bold text-ink">What's included in the Certified Marketplace?</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-[13px] text-body leading-relaxed">Verified, third-party stacks that have passed our vetting process (security, quality, no bloat). You can publish your own stacks and earn revenue share (70/30 split, 80/20 after 6 months for certified stacks).</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-[14px] font-bold text-ink">Does Claudient send my code anywhere?</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-[13px] text-body leading-relaxed">No. Everything runs locally. Skills are markdown files read by Claude Code on your machine. No telemetry unless you opt in. Enterprise customers can self-host in their own VPC.</p>
      </div>

